"{\"uid\": \"theportugalnews.com-news-2024-05-28-beware-of-the-olympic-scams-tips-that-every-portuguese-should-know-89255\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Read today's Portuguese stories delivered to your email.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 56, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13, \"end\": 23, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portuguese_language\", \"score\": 0.9999892413662871, \"rank\": 6.683303977217029e-06, \"text\": \"Portuguese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portuguese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portuguese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris are just around the corner.\", \"from\": 58, \"to\": 119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 86, \"end\": 91, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.3170854779956184e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans worldwide are excited about the global event.\", \"from\": 120, \"to\": 177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Although traveling to Paris allows you to witness athletic excellence, it also puts you at risk for scams.\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 200, \"end\": 205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.3170854779956184e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When traveling to the Olympics from Portugal, take the proper precautions to avoid following victim to cybercriminals.\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 321, \"end\": 329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\", \"score\": 0.9998069597118423, \"rank\": 0.0001395943611254774, \"text\": \"Portugal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ByAdvertiser,\\r                                                                 inPortugal,Sport\\u00b728 May 2024, 11:31\\u00b70 Comments    Like any other major sporting event, the Paris Olympics has become a breeding ground for various scams.\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 575, \"end\": 589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are the most common ones that Portuguese travelers need to be wary of:  Perhaps the most widespread scam, Olympic ticket fraud, involves the sale of counterfeit tickets.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 673, \"end\": 683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portuguese_language\", \"score\": 0.9999892413662871, \"rank\": 6.683303977217029e-06, \"text\": \"Portuguese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portuguese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portuguese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Scammers create convincing websites that mimic official ticketing platforms.\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The websites look legit, but they are designed to steal your credit card information.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One red flag you may notice is that they offer seats at heavily discounted prices.\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1058, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The scam site may promise guaranteed tickets, even when games are sold out.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you take this bait, you will end up having worthless tickets and will not be able to get your money back.\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Many fans wish to own a piece of Olympic memorabilia.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They often order shirts, hats, or photos to celebrate the event.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The desire to own a piece of the Olympics can also make fans vulnerable to merchandise scams.\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cybercriminals can set up fake websites or social media pages to sell \\\"official\\\" merchandise.\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Prices are typically heavily discounted on fake merchandise websites.\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Once you order, you may never receive the item or get a cheap, poorly made product instead.\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1715, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As fans flock to Paris from Portugal, scammers offer enticing deals for travel packages or accommodations.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1734, \"end\": 1739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.3170854779956184e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1745, \"end\": 1753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\", \"score\": 0.9998069597118423, \"rank\": 0.0001395943611254774, \"text\": \"Portugal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The counterfeit companies may ask for upfront payment and not provide any actual bookings.\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you fall victim to this type of scam, you may end up stranded and unable to reach your destination.\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To ensure your Olympic experience remains fun, consider the following best practices:  Always rely on official sources when purchasing tickets, merchandise, or booking travel.The Paris 2024 Olympics websiteis a good place to start if you plan to travel for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It offers authorized links to buy tickets, make travel arrangements, and order gear.\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you use a third-party seller, research their online reputation.\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Check out any reviews and verify that the website is legitimate.\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2509, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Customer feedback can reveal if there is anything suspicious about the seller.\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2588, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Use payment methods that offer fraud protection, like credit cards, whenever possible.\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you become a scam victim, you may dispute the charges and hopefully recover the lost money.\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2771, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not engage in emails, phone calls, or social media messages asking for personal information, like financial details.\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2892, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Legitimate organizations will never ask you to send payment details through messaging apps or email.\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If unsure, contact the company directly through official contact details.\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3067, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What is a VPN?A virtual private network encrypts your internet traffic, shielding your data from cyber threats.\", \"from\": 3069, \"to\": 3180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3079, \"end\": 3082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virtual_private_network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.74519677323798e-26, \"text\": \"VPN\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virtual_private_network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virtual_private_network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Using this cybersecurity tool can help to protect your online activities, such as financial transactions, during your trip to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3320, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Using a VPN while traveling to the Paris Olympics offers several advantages, including:  A VPN masks your IP address and encrypts your data in transit, making it difficult for internet service providers, advertisers, or third parties to track your online activities.\", \"from\": 3324, \"to\": 3590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3430, \"end\": 3440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IP_address\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.990546457863877e-26, \"text\": \"IP address\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IP_address\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IP_address\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Access to specific websites and online services may be restricted or censored in some countries.\", \"from\": 3592, \"to\": 3688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A VPN can help you bypass these geo-restrictions.\", \"from\": 3689, \"to\": 3738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While in Paris, you can still visit your favorite social media sites, news outlets, and streaming services.\", \"from\": 3739, \"to\": 3846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3748, \"end\": 3753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.3170854779956184e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Public Wi-Fi hotspots available around the Olympics will be an attraction point to hackers.\", \"from\": 3848, \"to\": 3939, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since a VPN encrypts your internet traffic, your login details, financial information, and other data will remain protected from the snoopers online.\", \"from\": 3940, \"to\": 4089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Prices for flights, hotels, and other travel expenses may vary depending on your location.\", \"from\": 4091, \"to\": 4181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can find the best prices for travel arrangements by connecting to VPN servers in different regions.\", \"from\": 4182, \"to\": 4285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just try to change your location from Portugal to any other country and compare the prices.\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4324, \"end\": 4332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\", \"score\": 0.9998069597118423, \"rank\": 0.0001395943611254774, \"text\": \"Portugal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To further enhance your protection, consider the following before and during your trip to the Paris Olympics:      The 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris promises to be a once-in-a-lifetime event, but Portuguese fans must watch out for scams that target travelers.\", \"from\": 4381, \"to\": 4640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4524, \"end\": 4529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.3170854779956184e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4577, \"end\": 4587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portuguese_language\", \"score\": 0.9999892413662871, \"rank\": 6.683303977217029e-06, \"text\": \"Portuguese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portuguese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portuguese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By understanding common Olympic scams, relying on official sources, and using a VPN, you can protect yourself from potentially high financial losses.\", \"from\": 4641, \"to\": 4790, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Share this article:Share  InPortugal,Lifestyle-29 Nov 2025, 18:59  InPortugal-29 Nov 2025, 17:01  InPortugal-28 Nov 2025, 10:01  We are proud to provide our readers from around the world with independent, honest and unbiased news for free - both online and in print.Our dedicated team supports the local community, foreign residents and visitors of all nationalities through our newspaper, website, social media and our newsletter.\", \"from\": 4792, \"to\": 5223, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We appreciate that not everyone can afford to pay for our services but if you are able to, we ask you tosupport The Portugal News by making a contribution - no matter how small.\", \"from\": 5225, \"to\": 5402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5337, \"end\": 5354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Portugal_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Portugal News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Portugal_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Portugal_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change how much you give or cancel your contributions at any time.\", \"from\": 5404, \"to\": 5478, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Be the first to comment on this article  InPortugal,Lifestyle-29 Nov 2025, 18:59  InPortugal-29 Nov 2025, 17:01  InPortugal-28 Nov 2025, 10:01  InNews,Portugal,Sport-31 May 2025, 08:02  InNews,Portugal,Sport-27 Feb 2025, 12:06  InNews,Portugal,Sport-03 Nov 2024, 12:02  InNews,Portugal,Sport-09 Sep 2024, 11:02  InNews-03 Sep 2024, 16:23  InNews-02 Sep 2024, 10:02  In  \\r                 -03 Dec 2025, 19:35  In  \\r                 -03 Dec 2025, 14:32  In  \\r           